</b></p>
<p><b>differences in salaries and other terms of employment between men and women 
</b></p>
<p><b>who perform work that is regarded as equal or equivalent (Croatia); 
</b></p>
<p>145.37. <b>Take concrete actions to end the increasing gender gap in the area of 
</b></p>
<p><b>employment and pay, thus ensuring equal remuneration for men and women 
</b></p>
<p><b>(South Africa); 
</b></p>
<p>145.38. <b>Continue efforts to further reduce the pay gap between women and 
</b></p>
<p><b>men (Albania); 
</b></p>
<p>145.39. <b>Take the necessary measures to reduce the gender wage gap 
</b></p>
